mages-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="弗兰西斯卡·阿梅乌达" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Romeo-and-Juliet-actress-backed-Photo-by-Ian-West_PA-Images-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>女演员弗兰西斯卡·阿梅乌达-里弗斯在公开信中表示支持，谴责她自出演<em>《罗密欧与朱丽叶》</em>以来所受到的“种族主义和厌恶女性的虐待”。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-whos-starring-opposite-tom-holland-in-romeo-juliet-3610850">宣布演员阵容</a>（其中还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-holland">汤姆·赫兰德）</a>之后，阿梅乌达-里弗斯遭到了网上的“猛烈攻击”。</p><p>作为回应，杰米·劳埃德公司发表声明，谴责“网上针对我们公司成员的一系列令人遗憾的种族虐待行为”。</p><p>他们继续说道：“这必须停止。我们正在与一群杰出的艺术家合作。我们坚持认为他们可以自由创作作品，而不会面临网络骚扰。”</p><p> “我们不会容忍任何虐待行为，并将予以举报。欺凌和骚扰在网上、在我们的行业或更广泛的社区中都没有立足之地，”该剧院公司写道。</p><p> “我们庆祝我们令人难以置信的合作者的非凡才华。<em>罗密欧与朱丽叶</em>社区将继续以慷慨和爱心排练，并专注于我们作品的创作。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5YSb6bIOey/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100